  "id": "ex_technical_4f4fd002",
  "intent": "Execute a comprehensive PCR amplification and purification workflow for EGFR pathway analysis: distribute master mix (user-defined volume) to 1-24 DNA samples at 4\u00b0C, perform PCR cycling (98\u00b0C initial denaturation, 4 cycles of 98\u00b0C/63\u00b0C/65\u00b0C, 23 cycles of 98\u00b0C/64\u00b0C, final extension at 65\u00b0C), conduct magnetic bead purification with dual 80% ethanol washes, perform indexing reaction at 37\u00b0C for 20 minutes, execute second magnetic purification, and elute final libraries in 20\u00b5L TE buffer with 4\u00b0C storage",
